Package: hydrateme
Version: 1.3.6-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pyqt6, python3-dbus, pulseaudio-utils, libnotify-bin
Maintainer: "Karan Kumar" <karankumarsacher@gmail.com>
Description: A desktop app that reminds you to drink water every 30 minutes
 A simple PyQt6 application that runs in the background
 and pops up a "force attention" window to remind you to hydrate.
 It integrates with GNOME screen lock to show notifications
 instead of a popup if you are away.
